{"tid":2464261,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"【影片】今日緬甸土瓦市軍警見騎士就開槍的實境","createTime":"2021-03-27T10:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-27T11:18:19.000Z","uid":310850,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a9a45d457f72f22ae265d62b9f557309b8e472cf","tid":2464261,"uid":310850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:22:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://fb.watch/4uMcYbvVAp/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.watch%2F4uMcYbvVAp%2F&d=jrWVSpMJYTM9%2F%2BTkK0Hr3z%2BdFj26OgxneTHruUJDv9o%3D&h=dda64074\" target=\"_blank\">https://fb.watch/4uMcYbvVAp/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n影片是今日土瓦市軍警見騎士就開槍的實境<br />\n<br />\n27號中午12:30分止<br />\n全國死亡人數已達51人<br />\nMagway瑪奎省Pwintbyu ပွင့်ဖြူ- 1<br />\nMagway瑪奎省Pakokku ပခုက္ကူ- 3<br />\nMagway瑪奎省Daik Uဒိုက်ဦး- 2<br />\n曼德勒省瓦城Mandalayမန္တလေး- 9<br />\n曼德勒省Meiktila မိတ်ထီလာ- 3<br />\n曼德勒省Kyaukpadaung ကျောက်ပန်းတောင်း- 3<br />\n曼德勒省Nyaung Uညောင်ဦး- 1<br />\n曼德勒省Pyin Oo Lwin မေမြို့- 2<br />\n曼德勒省敏強Myingyanမြင်းခြံ- 1<br />\nSagaing實皆省Shwebo ရွှေဘို- 1<br />\nSagaing 實皆省Sagaing စစ်ကိုင်း- 2<br />\nShan北撣邦腊戌Lashioလားရှိုး- 4<br />\nShan北撣邦木姐Museမူဆယ်- 1<br />\nMon孟邦Kyaikto ကျိုက်ထို- 2<br />\nTanintharyi 德寧達伊省Myeik丹老မြိတ်- 2<br />\nTanintharyi 德寧達伊省Dawei土瓦ထား၀ယ်- 1<br />\n仰光省Insein茵盛အင်းစိန်- 1<br />\n仰光省ဒလ Dalla  - 8<br />\nBago勃固省Pe New Koneပဲနွယ်ကုန်း (ပဲခူးတိုင်း)- 1<br />\nBago勃固省Hpa Doဖဒိုမြို့ (ပဲဲခူးတိုင်း)- 1"},{"pid":"bb2e1a1ae40a7fddc9df835d0c668e745333d504","tid":2464261,"uid":110509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:28:07.000Z","msg":"CLS"},{"pid":"3b2bd6d1c900d271bd3e7359cfe16f69cf49de46","tid":2464261,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-27T10:29:55.000Z","msg":"好似國定殺戮日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解冇人理佢地<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/